data.description:
Welcome Home!! This is your chance to escape the hustle of city life! 
Enjoy the peaceful surroundings from your own porch on this 10 acre ranch style home. Owner has updated all areas of this home inside and out. Granite countertops in kitchen and master bath. All interior walls and cabinets have been freshly repainted. Guest bathroom completely remodeled. Workshop with Stone veneer/metal roof attached carport. 30 Amp hook-up for an RV. Property has three padded areas prefect for livestock animals and includes a horse stall as well as an 8 x 12 shed with attached carport. The property also features storage. Both storages have solar light connections. Front gate entrances have solar light connections as well.
